import {
  Card,
  Row,
  Col,
  CardTitle,
  CardBody,
  Button,
  Form,
  FormGroup,
  Label,
  Input,
  FormText,
} from "reactstrap";



const Login = () => {
         
          
        
         
  return (
    <Row style={{marginTop: "auto", marginLeft: "left", marginRight: "right", justifyContent: "center"}}>
      <Col style={{ marginLeft: "left", marginRight: "right", justifyContent: "center"}}>
        <Card style={{width: "500px", marginLeft: "left", marginRight: "right", justifyContent: "center"}}>
          <CardTitle tag="h4" className=" p-3 " style={{textAlign: "center"}}>
           
            Iniciar Sesi√≥n
          </CardTitle>
          <CardBody>
          <Form  action="" method="POST" >
              <FormGroup >
                <Label for="exampleEmail">Nombre</Label>
                <Input
                  id="nombre"
                  name="nombre"
                  placeholder="nombre"
                  type="text"

                />
              </FormGroup>
              <FormGroup >
                <Label for="exampleEmail">Apellido</Label>
                <Input
                  id="apellido"
                  name="apellido"
                  placeholder="apellido"
                  type="text"
                />
              </FormGroup>
              <Button type="submit" style={{marginLeft: "auto", marginRight: "auto"}}>Ingresar</Button>
            </Form>
           
             
          </CardBody>
        </Card>
      </Col>
    </Row>
  );
};

export default Login;
